cern.extjfx.chart.data

Interface ChartData<X extends Number,Y extends Number>

  • Type Parameters:
    X - type of X values
    Y - type of Y values
    All Superinterfaces:
    Observable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayData, ListData

    public interface ChartData<X extends Number,Y extends Number>
extends Observable
    Holder for data (X and Y) that can be displayed in chart. The primary purpose of this interface is data reduction by the DataReducingObservableList.
